Tottenham beat Newcastle 3-1 at White Hart Lane on Sunday afternoon . 
  Nacer Chadli opened the scoring for the hosts in the 30th minute . 
  Jack Colback equalised for the Magpies before Christian Eriksen scored the winner . 
  Harry Kane scored his 30th goal of the season for Spurs . 
  Newcastle have now lost six games in a row for the first time in their history . 
 